title: Arris CMTS: Memory Usage
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/arris
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check shows the current and total memory usage of module in a Arris CMTS device.

 You configure upper levels for {WARN}/{CRIT} (default: 80.0/90.0)

 The service goes {WARN}/{CRIT} if the memory usage exceeds these levels.

 The check uses the CADANT-CMTS-EQUIPMENT-MIB.

item:
 The ID of the module

discovery:
 One service is created for each module
